ding:0;line-height:1.4;letter-spacing:0.1px;\">\n                      PG Department of Data Science &nbsp;&#8212;&nbsp; Official Placement Communication\n                    </p>\n                  </td>\n                </tr>\n              </table>\n\n              <!-- Three-column section -->\n              <table role=\"presentation\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\"\n                style=\"mso-table-lspace:0pt;mso-table-rspace:0pt;\">\n                <tr>\n\n                  <!-- Column 1 · Address -->\n                  <td valign=\"top\" width=\"34%\" style=\"width:34%;padding:20px 16px 20px 32px;\">\n                    <p style=\"font-family:\'Source Sans 3\',\'Source Sans Pro\',Arial,\'Helvetica Neue\',Helvetica,sans-serif;\n                             font-size:9.5px;font-weight:700;color:#5b9ec9;\n                             letter-spacing:1.1px;text-transform:uppercase;\n                             margin:0 0 9px 0;padding:0;\">\n                      Address\n                    </p>\n                    <p style=\"font-family:\'Source Sans 3\',\'Source Sans Pro\',Arial,\'Helvetica Neue\',Helvetica,sans-serif;\n                             font-size:11.5px;color:#dce8f0;line-height:1.85;\n                             margin:0;padding:0;\">\n                      30, Mother Teresa Sarani<br />\n                      Kolkata &#8212; 700016<br />\n                      West Bengal, India\n                    </p>\n                  </td>\n\n                  <!-- Column 2 · Contact -->\n                  <td valign=\"top\" width=\"33%\" style=\"width:33%;padding:20px 16px;border-left:1px solid #2e3f54;\">\n                    <p style=\"font-family:\'Source Sans 3\',\'Source Sans Pro\',Arial,\'Helvetica Neue\',Helvetica,sans-serif;\n                             font-size:9.5px;font-weight:700;color:#5b9ec9;\n                             letter-spacing:1.1px;text-transform:uppercase;\n                             margin:0 0 9px 0;padding:0;\">\n                      Contact\n                    </p>\n                    <p style=\"font-family:\'Source Sans 3\',\'Source Sans Pro\',Arial,\'Helvetica Neue\',Helvetica,sans-serif;\n                             font-size:11.5px;color:#dce8f0;line-height:1.85;\n                             margin:0;padding:0;\">\n                      <a href=\"tel:+919830275826\"\n                        style=\"color:#ffffff;text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:2px;\">+91-9830275826</a><br />\n                      <a href=\"mailto:datascience.placement@sxccal.edu\"\n                        style=\"color:#ffffff;text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:2px;word-break:break-all;\">datascience.placement@sxccal.edu</a><br />\n                      <a href=\"https://sxccal.edu/postgraduate-department-of-data-science\"\n                        style=\"color:#ffffff;text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:2px;\">www.sxccal.edu</a>\n                    </p>\n                  </td>\n\n                  <!-- Column 3 · Accreditations -->\n                  <td valign=\"top\" width=\"33%\"\n                    style=\"width:33%;padding:20px 32px 20px 16px;border-left:1px solid #2e3f54;\">\n                    <p style=\"font-family:\'Source Sans 3\',\'Source Sans Pro\',Arial,\'Helvetica Neue\',Helvetica,sans-serif;\n                             font-size:9.5px;font-weight:700;color:#5b9ec9;\n                             letter-spacing:1.1px;text-transform:uppercase;\n                             margin:0 0 9px 0;padding:0;\">\n                      Accreditations\n                    </p>\n                    <p style=\"font-family:\'Source Sans 3\',\'Source Sans Pro\',Arial,\'Helvetica Neue\',Helvetica,sans-serif;\n                             font-size:11.5px;color:#dce8f0;line-height:1.85;\n                             margin:0;padding:0;\">\n                      NAAC A++ (4th Cycle, 2024)<br />\n                      NIRF Rank 8 in India (2025)<br />\n                      ISO 9001:2015 Certified<br />\n                      College of Excellence (UGC)\n                    </p>\n                  </td>\n\n                </tr>\n              </table>\n\n              <!-- Divider -->\n              <table role=\"presentation\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\"\n                style=\"mso-table-lspace:0pt;mso-table-rspace:0pt;\">\n                <tr>\n                  <td style=\"border-top:1px solid #2e3f54;font-size:0;line-height:0;\">&#160;</td>\n                </tr>\n              </table>\n\n              <!-- Copyright bar -->\n              <table role=\"presentation\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\"\n                style=\"mso-table-lspace:0pt;mso-table-rspace:0pt;\">\n                <tr>\n                  <td style=\"padding:11px 32px 14px 32px;\">\n                    <p style=\"font-family:\'Source Sans 3\',\'Source Sans Pro\',Arial,\'Helvetica Neue\',Helvetica,sans-serif;\n                             font-size:10px;color:#6d8fa8;line-height:1.65;\n                             margin:0;padding:0;\">\n                      &#169; 2026 St. Xavier\'s College (Autonomous), Kolkata. All rights reserved.\n                      &nbsp;&#8226;&nbsp;\n                      This communication is intended solely for the named recipient and is authorised official\n                      correspondence of the PG Department of Data Science.\n                    </p>\n                  </td>\n                </tr>\n              </table>\n\n            </td>\n          </tr>\n          <!-- END FOOTER -->\n\n\n        </table>\n        <!-- END CARD -->\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </table>\n\n</body>\n\n</html>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 'sent', 0, '2026-03-02 07:14:15', '2026-03-02 07:14:15', '2026-03-02 07:14:15');
INSERT INTO `sent_emails_new` (`id`, `email_uuid`, `message_id`, `sender_email`, `sender_name`, `recipient_email`, `cc_list`, `bcc_list`, `reply_to`, `subject`, `article_title`, `body_text`, `body_html`, `label_id`, `label_name`, `label_color`, `has_attachments`, `email_type`, `is_deleted`, `sent_at`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(245, 'c377d9dc-1043-4d5f-a882-f954765c51cc', NULL, 'datascience.placement@sxccal.edu', 'Dr. Durba Bhattacharya', 'vignesh.vijayakumar@freshworks.com', '', '', NULL, 'Campus Placement Invitation | M.Sc. Data Science | St. Xavier’s College Kolkata', 'Campus Placement Invitation | M.Sc. Data Science | St. Xavier’s College Kolkata', 'St. Xavier\'s College — Official Placement Communication body, #bodyWrap { margin: 0 !important; padding: 0 !important; width: 100% !important; background-color: #eef1f5 !important; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; } table { border-collapse: collapse !important; mso-table-lspace: 0pt !important; mso-table-rspace: 0pt !important; } img { border: 0; outline: none; text-decoration: none; -ms-interpolation-mode: bicubic; display: block; } a { text-decoration: none; } .card { width: 600px; }     St. Xavier’s College (Autonomous), Kolkata Ranked 8th in India — NIRF 2025 Autonomous College (2006) · College of Excellence · NAAC A++ (4th Cycle, 2024) · ISO 9001:2015 Official Invitation — Campus Recruitment, MSc Data Science 2026   Connect With Us Student Brochure Student CV Campus Placement Invitation | M.Sc. Data Science | St. Xavier’s College Kolkata   Dear Vignesh Vijayakumar, I’m reaching out to discuss potential collaboration with Freshworks for campus placement opportunities for our M.Sc. in Data Science (Batch 2024–2026). With St. Xavier’s College being ranked 8th nationally by NIRF 2025 and designated as a College of Excellence by the UGC, St. Xavier’s College is among the leading institutions in the country. Our M.Sc. program in Data Science is designed with a strong interdisciplinary foundation, integrating Statistics, Computer Science, Mathematics, and applied analytics, with emphasis on practical implementation through projects and industry exposure. Students are trained in areas including: Data Analysis & Statistical Modeling · Machine Learning & Predictive Analytics · Data Engineering Fundamentals · Business Intelligence & Visualization · Applied AI & Emerging Technologies Depending on your organization’s requirements, our students are prepared to contribute across analytics, technology, research, or data-driven decision-support roles. For your reference, we have attached the student profiles and placement brochure to this email. We would be grateful for the opportunity to understand your hiring needs and explore whether our students may align with your current or upcoming requirements. If convenient, we would be happy to share further details or arrange a brief discussion at your preferred time. Thank you for your time and consideration. Warm Regards Dr. Durba Bhattacharya Head of Department, Data Science St. Xavier\'s College (Autonomous), Kolkata   In the Spotlight Departmental Achievements Article Convergence successfully concluded, marking the launch of Gradient\'s début edition. Read Here → 17 February 2026', '<!DOCTYPE html\n  PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN\" \"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd\">\n<html xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" xmlns:v=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:vml\"\n  xmlns:o=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" lang=\"en\">\n\n<head>\n  <meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\" />\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\" />\n  <meta name=\"x-apple-disable-message-reformatting\" />\n  <meta http-equiv=\"X-UA-Compatible\" content=\"IE=edge\" />\n  <title>St. Xavier\'s College — Official Placement Communication</title>\n\n  <!-- Google Fonts: Source Sans 3 + Merriweather — closest to Nature/Springer Nature web stack -->\n  <link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com\">\n  <link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.gstatic.com\" crossorigin>\n  <link\n    href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Source+Sans+3:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,600;0,700;1,400&family=Merriweather:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,700;1,300;1,400&dis