ans 3\',\'Source Sans Pro\',Arial,\'Helvetica Neue\',Helvetica,sans-serif;\n                               font-size:10px;color:#999999;margin:0;padding:0;\">\n                        17 February 2026\n                      </p>\n                    </a>\n                  </td>\n\n\n                  <!-- Item 2 -->\n                  <td valign=\"top\" width=\"33%\"\n                    style=\"width:33%;padding-left:9px;padding-right:9px;border-right:1px solid #d8d8d8;\"\">\n                    <a href=\"\n                    https://www.linkedin.com/posts/pgds-sxccal_powerquest2025-datascience-sxckolkata-activity-7309782682471751680-GZPq/\"\n                    style=\"text-decoration:none;color:inherit;display:block;\">\n\n                    <img src=\"https://hr.holidayseva.com/Assets/image/pharmaquant.png\" alt=\"PharmaQuant Hackathon\"\n                      style=\"width:100%;height:102px;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;display:block;border-radius:3px;\">\n\n                    <p style=\"font-family:\'Source Sans 3\',\'Source Sans Pro\',Arial,\'Helvetica Neue\',Helvetica,sans-serif;\n                               font-size:9.5px;font-weight:700;color:#c6613f;\n                               letter-spacing:0.8px;text-transform:uppercase;\n                               margin:10px 0 5px 0;padding:0;\">\n                      Hackathon\n                    </p>\n                    <p style=\"font-family:Merriweather,Georgia,\'Times New Roman\',Times,serif;\n                               font-size:12.5px;color:#111111;line-height:1.55;\n                               margin:0 0 8px 0;padding:0;\">\n                      Emerged as Top Team and Second Runner-Up at the\n                      <strong>PharmaQuant</strong> Hackathon.\n                    </p>\n                    <p style=\"font-family:\'Source Sans 3\',\'Source Sans Pro\',Arial,\'Helvetica Neue\',Helvetica,sans-serif;\n                               font-size:10px;color:#226799;font-weight:600;\n                               margin:0 0 8px 0;padding:0;\">\n                      View Post &#8594;\n                    </p>\n                    <p style=\"font-family:\'Source Sans 3\',\'Source Sans Pro\',Arial,\'Helvetica Neue\',Helvetica,sans-serif;\n                               font-size:10px;color:#999999;margin:0;padding:0;\">\n                      22 March 2025\n                    </p>\n                    </a>\n                  </td>\n                  <!-- Item 3 -->\n                  <td valign=\"top\" width=\"34%\" style=\"width:34%;padding-left:9px;\">\n                    <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/posts/pgds-sxccal_congratulations-demandforecasting-hackathon-activity-7347106714988494850-ruDL\"\n                      style=\"text-decoration:none;color:inherit;display:block;\">\n\n                      <img src=\"https://hr.holidayseva.com/Assets/image/sannidhya.png\" alt=\"MOSPI Hackathon\"\n                        style=\"width:100%;height:102px;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;display:block;border-radius:3px;\">\n\n                      <p style=\"font-family:\'Source Sans 3\',\'Source Sans Pro\',Arial,\'Helvetica Neue\',Helvetica,sans-serif;\n                               font-size:9.5px;font-weight:700;color:#c6613f;\n                               letter-spacing:0.8px;text-transform:uppercase;\n                               margin:10px 0 5px 0;padding:0;\">\n                        MOSPI\n                      </p>\n                      <p style=\"font-family:Merriweather,Georgia,\'Times New Roman\',Times,serif;\n                               font-size:12.5px;color:#111111;line-height:1.55;\n                               margin:0 0 8px 0;padding:0;\">\n                        Sannidhya Das secured a top-10 national rank in the\n                        <strong>MOSPI</strong> Hackathon.\n                      </p>\n                      <p style=\"font-family:\'Source Sans 3\',\'Source Sans Pro\',Arial,\'Helvetica Neue\',Helvetica,sans-serif;\n                               font-size:10px;color:#226799;font-weight:600;\n                               margin:0 0 8px 0;padding:0;\">\n                        View Post &#8594;\n                      </p>\n                      <p style=\"font-family:\'Source Sans 3\',\'Source Sans Pro\',Arial,\'Helvetica Neue\',Helvetica,sans-serif;\n                               font-size:10px;color:#999999;margin:0;padding:0;\">\n                        19 December 2022\n                      </p>\n                    </a>\n                  </td>\n\n\n                </tr>\n              </table>\n            </td>\n          </tr>\n          <!-- END DEPARTMENTAL ACHIEVEMENTS -->\n\n\n\n\n\n          <!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════\n             BLOCK 7 · FOOTER  (Nature.com-inspired, high-contrast)\n        ══════════════════════════════════════════ -->\n          <tr>\n            <td style=\"background-color:#192231;padding:0;border-top:3px solid #226799;\">\n\n              <!-- Institution nameplate -->\n              <table role=\"presentation\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\"\n                style=\"mso-table-lspace:0pt;mso-table-rspace:0pt;\">\n                <tr>\n                  <td style=\"padding:20px 32px 16px 32px;border-bottom:1px solid #2e3f54;\">\n                    <p style=\"font-family:\'Source Sans 3\',\'Source Sans Pro\',Arial,\'Helvetica Neue\',Helvetica,sans-serif;\n                             font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#ffffff;\n                             letter-spacing:0.3px;margin:0;padding:0;line-height:1.3;\">\n                      St. Xavier\'s College (Autonomous), Kolkata\n                    </p>\n                    <p style=\"font-family:\'Source Sans 3\',\'Source Sans Pro\',Arial,\'Helvetica Neue\',Helvetica,sans-serif;\n                             font-size:11px;color:#90aec6;\n                             margin:4px 0 0 0;padding:0;line-height:1.4;letter-spacing:0.1px;\">\n                      PG Department of Data Science &nbsp;&#8212;&nbsp; Official Placement Communication\n                    </p>\n                  </td>\n                </tr>\n              </table>\n\n              <!-- Three-column section -->\n              <table role=\"presentation\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\"\n                style=\"mso-table-lspace:0pt;mso-table-rspace:0pt;\">\n                <tr>\n\n                  <!-- Column 1 · Address -->\n                  <td valign=\"top\" width=\"34%\" style=\"width:34%;padding:20px 16px 20px 32px;\">\n                    <p style=\"font-family:\'Source Sans 3\',\'Source Sans Pro\',Arial,\'Helvetica Neue\',Helvetica,sans-serif;\n                             font-size:9.5px;font-weight:700;color:#5b9ec9;\n                             letter-spacing:1.1px;text-transform:uppercase;\n                             margin:0 0 9px 0;padding:0;\">\n                      Address\n                    </p>\n                    <p style=\"font-family:\'Source Sans 3\',\'Source Sans Pro\',Arial,\'Helvetica Neue\',Helvetica,sans-serif;\n                             font-size:11.5px;color:#dce8f0;line-height:1.85;\n                             margin:0;padding:0;\">\n                      30, Mother Teresa Sarani<br />\n                      Kolkata &#8212; 700016<br />\n                      West Bengal, India\n                    </p>\n                  </td>\n\n                  <!-- Column 2 · Contact -->\n                  <td valign=\"top\" width=\"33%\" style=\"width:33%;padding:20px 16px;border-left:1px solid #2e3f54;\">\n                    <p style=\"font-family:\'Source Sans 3\',\'Source Sans Pro\',Arial,\'Helvetica Neue\',Helvetica,sans-serif;\n                             font-size:9.5px;font-weight:700;color:#5b9ec9;\n                             letter-spacing:1.1px;text-transform:uppercase;\n                             margin:0 0 9px 0;padding:0;\">\n                      Contact\n                    </p>\n                    <p style=\"font-family:\'Source Sans 3\',\'Source Sans Pro\',Arial,\'Helvetica Neue\',Helvetica,sans-serif;\n                             font-size:11.5px;color:#dce8f0;line-height:1.85;\n                             margin:0;padding:0;\">\n                      <a href=\"tel:+919830275826\"\n                        style=\"color:#ffffff;text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:2px;\">+91-9830275826</a><br />\n                      <a href=\"mailto:datascience.placement@sxccal.edu\"\n                        style=\"color:#ffffff;text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:2px;word-break:break-all;\">datascience.placement@sxccal.edu</a><br />\n                      <a href=\"https://sxccal.edu/postgraduate-department-of-data-science\"\n                        style=\"color:#ffffff;text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:2px;\">www.sxccal.edu</a>\n                    </p>\n                  </td>\n\n                  <!-- Column 3 · Accreditations -->\n                  <td valign=\"top\" width=\"33%\"\n                    style=\"width:33%;padding:20px 32px 20px 16px;border-left:1px solid #2e3f54;\">\n                    <p style=\"font-family:\'Source Sans 3\',\'Source Sans Pro\',Arial,\'Helvetica Neue\',Helvetica,sans-serif;\n                             font-size:9.5px;font-weight:700;color:#5b9ec9;\n                             letter-spacing:1.1px;text-transform:uppercase;\n                             margin:0 0 9px 0;padding:0;\">\n                      Accreditations\n                    </p>\n                    <p style=\"font-family:\'Source Sans 3\',\'Source Sans Pro\',Arial,\'Helvetica Neue\',Helvetica,sans-serif;\n                             font-size:11.5px;color:#dce8f0;line-height:1.85;\n                             margin:0;padding:0;\">\n                      NAAC A++ (4th Cycle, 2024)<br />\n                      NIRF Rank 8 in India (2025)<br />\n                      ISO 9001:2015 Certified<br />\n                      College of Excellence (UGC)\n                    </p>\n                  </td>\n\n                </tr>\n              </table>\n\n              <!-- Divider -->\n              <table role=\"presentation\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\"\n                style=\"mso-table-lspace:0pt;mso-table-rspace:0pt;\">\n                <tr>\n                  <td style=\"border-top:1px solid #2e3f54;font-size:0;line-height:0;\">&#160;</td>\n                </tr>\n              </table>\n\n              <!-- Copyright bar -->\n              <table role=\"presentation\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\"\n                style=\"mso-table-lspace:0pt;mso-table-rspace:0pt;\">\n                <tr>\n                  <td style=\"padding:11px 32px 14px 32px;\">\n                    <p style=\"font-family:\'Source Sans 3\',\'Source Sans Pro\',Arial,\'Helvetica Neue\',Helvetica,sans-serif;\n                             font-size:10px;color:#6d8fa8;line-height:1.65;\n                             margin:0;padding:0;\">\n                      &#169; 2026 St. Xavier\'s College (Autonomous), Kolkata. All rights reserved.\n                      &nbsp;&#8226;&nbsp;\n                      This communication is intended solely for the named recipient and is authorised official\n                      correspondence of the PG Department of Data Science.\n                    </p>\n                  </td>\n                </tr>\n              </table>\n\n            </td>\n          </tr>\n          <!-- END FOOTER -->\n\n\n        </table>\n        <!-- END CARD -->\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </table>\n\n</body>\n\n</html>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 'sent', 0, '2026-03-02 07:14:44', '2026-03-02 07:14:44', '2026-03-02 07:14:44');
INSERT INTO `sent_emails_new` (`id`, `email_uuid`, `message_id`, `sender_email`, `sender_name`, `recipient_email`, `cc_list`, `bcc_list`, `reply_to`, `subject`, `article_title`, `body_text`, `body_html`, `label_id`, `label_name`, `label_color`, `has_attachments`, `email_type`, `is_deleted`, `sent_at`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(253, '1f16f0bb-8066-4fc8-9882-347b0cfe77d0', NULL, 'datascience.placement@sxccal.edu', 'Dr. Durba Bhattacharya', 'beejal.das@hdfcbank.com', '', '', NULL, 'Campus Placement Invitation | M.Sc. Data Science | St. Xavier’s College Kolkata', 'Campus Placement Invitation | M.Sc. Data Science | St. Xavier’s College Kolkata', 'St. Xavier\'s College — Official Placement Communication body, #bodyWrap { margin: 0 !important; padding: 0 !important; width: 100% !important; background-color: #eef1f5 !important; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; } table { border-collapse: collapse !important; mso-table-lspace: 0pt !important; mso-table-rspace: 0pt !important; } img { border: 0; outline: none; text-decoration: none; -ms-interpolation-mode: bicubic; display: block; } a { text-decoration: none; } .card { width: 600px; }     St. Xavier’s College (Autonomous), Kolkata Ranked 8th in India — NIRF 2025 Autonomous College (2006) · College of Excellence · NAAC A++ (4th Cycle, 2024) · ISO 9001:2015 Official Invitation — Campus Recruitment, MSc Data Science 2026   Connect With Us Student Brochure Student CV Campus Placement Invitation | M.Sc. Data Science | St. Xavier’s College Kolkata   Dear Beejal Das, I’m reaching out to discuss potential collaboration with HDFC for campus placement opportunities for our M.Sc. in Data Science (Batch 2024–2026). With St. Xavier’s College being ranked 8th nationally by NIRF 2025 and designated as a College of Excellence by the UGC, St. Xavier’s College is among the leading institutions in the country. Our M.Sc. program in Data Science is designed with a strong interdisciplinary foundation, integrating Statistics, Computer Science, Mathematics, and applied analytics, with emphasis on practical implementation through projects and industry exposure. Students are trained in areas including: Data Analysis & Statistical Modeling · Machine Learning & Predictive Analytics · Data Engineering Fundamentals · Business Intelligence & Visualization · Applied AI & Emerging Technologies Depending on your organization’s requirements, our students are prepared to contribute across analytics, technology, research, or data-driven decision-support roles. For your reference, we have attached the student profiles and placement brochure to this email. We would be grateful for the opportunity to understand your hiring needs and explore whether our students may align with your current or upcoming requirements. If convenient, we would be happy to share further details or arrange a brief discussion at your preferred time. Thank you for your time and consideration. Warm Regards Dr. Durba Bhattacharya Head of Department, Data Science St. Xavier\'s College (Autonomous), Kolkata   In the Spotlight Departmental Achievements Article Convergence successfully concluded, marking the launch of Gradient\'s début edition. Read Here → 17 February 2026', '<!DOCTYPE html\n  PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN\" \"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd\">\n<html xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" xmlns:v=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:vml\"\n  xmlns:o=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" lang=\"en\">\n\n<head>\n  <meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\" />\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\" />\n  <meta name=\"x-apple-disable-message-reformatting\" />\n  <meta http-equiv=\"X-UA-Compatible\" content=\"IE=edge\" />\n  <title>St. Xavier\'s College — Official Placement Communication</title>\n\n  <!-- Google Fonts: Source Sans 3 + Merriweather — closest to Nature/Springer Nature web stack -->\n  <link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com\">\n  <link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.gstatic.com\" crossorigin>\n  <link\n    href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Source+Sans+3:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,600;0,700;1,400&family=Merriweather:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,700;1,300;1,400&display=swap\"\n    rel=\"stylesheet\">\n\n  <!--[if mso]>\n  <xml>\n    <o:OfficeDocumentSettings>\n      <o:AllowPNG/>\n      <o:PixelsPerInch>96</o:PixelsPerInch>\n    </o:OfficeDocumentSettings>\n  </xml>\n  <![endif]-->\n\n  <style type=\"text/css\">\n    body,\n    #bodyWrap {\n      margin: 0 !important;\n      padding: 0 !important;\n      width: 100% !important;\n      background-color: #eef1f5 !important;\n      -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\n      -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;\n    }\n\n    table {\n      border-collapse: collapse !important;\n      mso-table-lspace: 0pt !important;\n      mso-table-rspace: 0pt !important;\n    }\n\n    img {\n      border: 0;\n      outline: none;\n      text-decoration: none;\n      -ms-interpolation-mode: bicubic;\n      display: block;\n    }\n\n    a {\n      text-decoration: none;\n    }\n\n    .card {\n      width: 600px;\n    }\n  </style>\n</head>\n\n<body style=\"margin:0;padding:0;background-color:#eef1f5;\">\n\n  <table role=\"presentation\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\" id=\"bodyWrap\"\n    style=\"background-color:#eef1f5;width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;mso-table-lspace:0pt;mso-table-rspace:0pt;\">\n    <tr>\n      <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding-top:28px;padding-bottom:28px;padding-left:0;padding-right:0;\">\n\n        <!-- CARD -->\n        <table class=\"card\" role=\"presentation\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"600\" style=\"width:600px;background-color:#ffffff;border:1px solid #d5dde8;border-radius:4px;\n               mso-table-lspace:0pt;mso-table-rspace:0pt;\">\n\n\n          <!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════\n             BLOCK 1 · HEADER\n        ══════════════════════════════════════════ -->\n          <tr>\n            <td style=\"background-color:#ffffff;border-bottom:1px solid #E6ECF5;padding:0;\">\n              <table role=\"presentation\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\"\n                style=\"mso-table-lspace:0pt;mso-table-rspace:0pt;\">\n                <tr>\n\n                  <td width=\"32\" style=\"width:32px;min-width:32px;font-size:0;line-height:0;\">&#160;</td>\n\n                  <!-- Logo -->\n                  <td valign=\"middle\" width=\"88\"\n                    style=\"width:88px;min-width:88px;padding-top:28px;padding-bottom:28px;\">\n                    <img src=\"https://hr.holidayseva.com/Assets/image/sxc_logo.png\" alt=\"SXC Logo\" width=\"78\"\n                      style=\"display:block;width:78px;\" />\n                  </td>\n\n                  <td width=\"20\" style=\"width:20px;font-size:0;line-height:0;\">&#160;</td>\n\n                  <!-- Text column -->\n                  <td valign=\"middle\" style=\"padding-top:26px;padding-bottom:26px;\">\n                    <table role=\"presentation\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\"\n                      style=\"mso-table-lspace:0pt;mso-table-rspace:0pt;\">\n\n                      <!-- Tier 1 · College name — primary visual anchor -->\n                      <tr>\n                        <td style=\"padding-bottom:10px;\">\n                          <p style=\"font-family:\'Source Sans 3\',\'Source Sans Pro\',Arial,\'Helvetica Neue\',Helvetica,sans-serif;\n                                   font-size:22px;font-weight:600;color:#0A1F44;\n                                   line-height:1.15;letter-spacing:0.1px;margin:0;padding:0;\">\n                            St. Xavier&#8217;s College (Autonomous), Kolkata\n                          </p>\n                        </td>\n                      </tr>\n\n                      <!-- Tier 2 · NIRF badge — secondary element, close to title -->\n                      <tr>\n                        <td style=\"padding-bottom:10px;\">\n                          <table role=\"presentation\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"\n                            style=\"mso-table-lspace:0pt;mso-table-rspace:0pt;\">\n                            <tr>\n                              <td style=\"background-color:#0F4C81;border-radius:5px;padding:5px 12px;\">\n                                <span style=\"font-family:\'Source Sans 3\',\'Source Sans Pro\',Arial,\'Helvetica Neue\',Helvetica,sans-serif;\n                                            font-size:10.5px;font-weight:600;color:#ffffff;\n                                            letter-spacing:0.3px;white-space:nowrap;\">\n                                  Ranked 8th in India &#8212; NIRF 2025\n                                </span>\n                              </td>\n                            </tr>\n                          </table>\n                        </td>\n                      </tr>\n\n                      <!-- Tier 3 · Accreditation — supporting text, reduced weight -->\n                      <tr>\n                        <td style=\"padding-bottom:14px;\">\n                          <p style=\"font-family:\'Source Sans 3\',\'Source Sans Pro\',Arial,\'Helvetica Neue\',Helvetica,sans-serif;\n                                   font-size:10px;font-weight:400;color:#9aafca;\n                                   line-height:1.6;margin:0;padding:0;letter-spacing:0.1px;\">\n                            Autonomous College (2006)&#160;&#183;&#160;College of Excellence&#160;&#183;&#160;NAAC A++\n                            (4th Cycle, 2024)&#160;&#183;&#160;ISO 9001:2015\n                          </p>\n                        </td>\n                      </tr>\n\n                      <!-- Tier 4 · Official invitation — ceremonial badge -->\n                      <tr>\n                        <td>\n                          <table role=\"presentation\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"\n                            style=\"mso-table-lspace:0pt;mso-table-rspace:0pt;\">\n                            <tr>\n                              <td\n                                style=\"background-color:rgba(159,42,36,0.06);border:1.5px solid #9F2A24;border-radius:7px;padding:7px 14px;\">\n                                <span style=\"font-family:\'Source Sans 3\',\'Source Sans Pro\',Arial,\'Helvetica Neue\',Helvetica,sans-serif;\n                                            font-size:10.5px;font-weight:600;color:#9F2A24;\n                                            letter-spacing:0.2px;white-space:nowrap;\">\n                                  Official Invitation &#8212; Campus Recruitment, MSc Data Science 2026\n                                </span>\n                              </td>\n                            </tr>\n                          </table>\n                        </td>\n                      </tr>\n\n                    </table>\n                  </td>\n\n                  <td width=\"32\" style=\"width:32px;min-width:32px;font-size:0;line-height:0;\">&#160;</td>\n\n                </tr>\n              </table>\n            </td>\n          </tr>\n          <!-- END HEADER -->\n\n\n          <!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════\n             BLOCK 2 · ACTION BAR\n        ══════════════════════════════════════════ -->\n          <tr>\n            <td style=\"background-color:#f5f8fc;border-bottom:1px solid #E6ECF5;padding:13px 20px;\">\n              <table role=\"presentation\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\"\n                style=\"mso-table-lspace:0pt;mso-table-rspace:0pt;\">\n                <tr>\n\n                  <!-- BTN 1 · Connect With Us — solid navy -->\n                  <td valign=\"middle\" width=\"33%\" style=\"width:33%;padding-right:7px;\">\n                    <table role=\"presentation\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\"\n                      style=\"mso-table-lspace:0pt;mso-table-rspace:0pt;\">\n                      <tr>\n                        <td style=\"background-color:#0A1F44;border-radius:8px;\n                                   box-shadow:0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);\">\n                          <a href=\"mailto:datascience.placement@sxccal.edu?subject=Re%3A%20Campus%20Placement%20%E2%80%93%20M.Sc.%20Data%20Science%20%7C%20St.%20Xavier%27s%20College&body=Dear%20Placement%20Team%2C%0A%0AThank%20you%20for%20reaching%20out%20to%20us%20at%20HDFC.%20We%20have%20reviewed%20your%20email%20regarding%20the%20M.Sc.%20Data%20Science%20placement%20opportunities%20and%20would%20like%20to%20respond%20accordingly.%0A%0ABest%20regards%2C%0ABeejal Das%0AHDFC\"\n                            style=\"display:block;text-decoration:none;padding:12px 16px;\">\n                            <table role=\"presentation\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"\n                              style=\"mso-table-lspace:0pt;mso-table-rspace:0pt;margin:0 auto;\">\n                              <tr>\n                                <td valign=\"middle\" style=\"padding-right:9px;\">\n                                  <img src=\"https://hr.holidayseva.com/Assets/icons/connect.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"20\"\n                                    height=\"20\" style=\"display:block;width:20px;height:20px;\">\n                                </td>\n                                <td valign=\"middle\">\n                                  <p style=\"font-family:\'Source Sans 3\',\'Source Sans Pro\',Arial,\'Helvetica Neue\',Helvetica,sans-serif;\n                                           font-size:12.5px;font-weight:600;color:#ffffff;\n                                           margin:0;padding:0;line-height:1;white-space:nowrap;\">\n                                    Connect With Us\n                                  </p>\n                                </td>\n                              </tr>\n                            </table>\n                          </a>\n                        </td>\n                      </tr>\n                    </table>\n                  </td>\n\n                  <!-- BTN 2 · Student Brochure — outline -->\n                  <td valign=\"middle\" width=\"34%\" style=\"width:34%;padding-left:7px;padding-right:7px;\">\n                    <table role=\"presentation\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\"\n                      style=\"mso-table-lspace:0pt;mso-table-rspace:0pt;\">\n                      <tr>\n                        <td style=\"background-color:#ffffff;border:1.5px solid #D7E2F1;border-radius:8px;\n                                   box-shadow:0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);\">\n                          <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/174oZ7Ls_x9JrYu_4Zp45mRxEsI_8szIT/\"\n                            style=\"display:block;text-decoration:none;padding:12px 16px;\">\n                            <table role=\"presentation\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"\n                              style=\"mso-table-lspace:0pt;mso-table-rspace:0pt;margin:0 auto;\">\n                              <tr>\n                                <td valign=\"middle\" style=\"padding-right:9px;\">\n                                  <img src=\"https://hr.holidayseva.com/Assets/icons/card.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"20\"\n                                    height=\"20\" style=\"display:block;width:20px;height:20px;\">\n                                </td>\n                                <td valign=\"middle\">\n                                  <p style=\"font-family:\'Source Sans 3\',\'Source Sans Pro\',Arial,\'Helvetica Neue\',Helvetica,sans-serif;\n                                           font-size:12.5px;font-weight:600;color:#0A1F44;\n                                           margin:0;padding:0;line-height:1;white-space:nowrap;\">\n                                    Student Brochure\n                                  </p>\n                                </td>\n                              </tr>\n                            </table>\n                          </a>\n                        </td>\n                      </tr>\n                    </table>\n                  </td>\n\n                  <!-- BTN 3 · Student CV — outline -->\n                  <td valign=\"middle\" width=\"33%\" style=\"width:33%;padding-left:7px;\">\n                    <table role=\"presentation\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\"\n                      style=\"mso-table-lspace:0pt;mso-table-rspace:0pt;\">\n                      <tr>\n                        <td style=\"background-color:#ffffff;border:1.5px solid #D7E2F1;border-radius:8px;\n                                   box-shadow:0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);\">\n                          <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1wwFKofEPonaXrrxoBIRhdCRDHKiRNMfV/\"\n                            style=\"display:block;text-decoration:none;padding:12px 16px;\">\n                            <table role=\"presentation\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"\n                              style=\"mso-table-lspace:0pt;mso-table-rspace:0pt;margin:0 auto;\">\n                              <tr>\n                                <td valign=\"middle\" style=\"padding-right:9px;\">\n                                  <img src=\"https://hr.holidayseva.com/Assets/icons/download.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"20\"\n                                    height=\"20\" style=\"display:block;width:20px;height:20px;\">\n                                </td>\n                                <td valign=\"middle\">\n                                  <p style=\"font-family:\'Source Sans 3\',\'Source Sans Pro\',Arial,\'Helvetica Neue\',Helvetica,sans-serif;\n                                           font-size:12.5px;font-weight:600;color:#0A1F44;\n                                           margin:0;padding:0;line-height:1;white-space:nowrap;\">\n                                    Student CV\n                                  </p>\n                                </td>\n                              </tr>\n                            </table>\n                          </a>\n                        </td>\n                      </tr>\n                    </table>\n                  </td>\n\n                </tr>\n              </table>\n            </td>\n          </tr>\n          <!-- END ACTION BAR -->\n\n\n          <!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════\n             BLOCK 3 · ARTICLE TITLE SECTION — Bold & Authoritative\n        ══════════════════════════════════════════ -->\n          <tr>\n            <td style=\"padding:0px 32px 0 32px;background-color:#ffffff;\">\n              <!-- Article type + date — muted grey metadata row -->\n              <p style=\"font-family:\'Source Sans 3\',\'Source Sans Pro\',Arial,\'Helvetica Neue\',Helvetica,sans-serif;\n                       font-size:11px;color:#767676;letter-spacing:0.2px;\n                       margin:0 0 12px 0;padding:0;line-height:1.5;\">\n                <!-- Invitation &#183; Open Access &nbsp;&nbsp;|&nbsp;&nbsp; 25 February 2026 -->\n              </p>\n              <!-- Title — large, bold, authoritative -->\n              <p style=\"font-family:\'Source Sans 3\',\'Source Sans Pro\',Arial,\'Helvetica Neue\',Helvetica,sans-serif;\n                       font-size:28px;font-weight:800;color:#0d2a47;\n                       line-height:1.3;letter-spacing:-0.4px;\n                       margin:0 0 0 0;padding:0;\">\n                Campus Placement Invitation | M.Sc. Data Science | St. Xavier’s College Kolkata\n              </p>\n            </td>\n          </tr>\n\n          <!-- Thick rule below title -->\n          <tr>\n            <td style=\"padding:20px 32px 0 32px;background-color:#ffffff;\">\n              <table role=\"presentation\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\"\n                style=\"mso-table-lspace:0pt;mso-table-rspace:0pt;\">\n                <tr>\n                  <td style=\"border-top:2px solid #226799;font-size:0;line-height:0;\">&#160;</td>\n                </tr>\n              </table>\n            </td>\n          </tr>\n          <!-- END ARTICLE TITLE SECTION -->\n\n\n          <!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════\n             BLOCK 4 · BODY — Original content with parameters\n        ══════════════════════════════════════════ -->\n          <tr>\n            <td style=\"padding:28px 32px 0 32px;background-color:#ffffff;\">\n\n              <p style=\"font-family:Merriweather,Georgia,\'Times New Roman\',Times,serif;\n                       font-size:15.5px;color:#222222;line-height:1.85;\n                       margin:0 0 16px 0;padding:0;font-weight:600;\">\n                Dear Beejal Das,\n              </p>\n\n              <p style=\"font-family:Merriweather,Georgia,\'Times New Roman\',Times,serif;\n                       font-size:15.5px;color:#333333;line-height:1.9;\n                       margin:0 0 16px 0;padding:0;\">\n                I’m reaching out to discuss potential collaboration with <strong>HDFC</strong> for campus\n                placement opportunities for our M.Sc. in Data Science (Batch 2024&#8211;2026).\n              </p>\n\n              <p style=\"font-family:Merriweather,Georgia,\'Times New Roman\',Times,serif;\n                       font-size:15.5px;color:#333333;line-height:1.9;\n                       margin:0 0 16px 0;padding:0;\">\n                With St. Xavier’s College being <span style=\"color:#b74727;\">ranked 8th nationally by\n                  NIRF 2025 </span> and\n                designated as a\n                <span style=\"color:#b74727;\">College of Excellence by the UGC,</span>\n                St.&#160;Xavier&#8217;s College is\n                among the\n                leading institutions in the country. Our M.Sc. program in Data Science is designed with\n                a strong\n                interdisciplinary foundation, integrating Statistics, Computer Science, Mathematics, and\n                applied\n                analytics, with emphasis on practical implementation through projects and industry\n                exposure.\n              </p>\n\n              <!-- Skills heading — Nature-style subdued label -->\n              <p style=\"font-family:\'Source Sans 3\',\'Source Sans Pro\',Arial,\'Helvetica Neue\',Helvetica,sans-serif;\n                       font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:#226799;\n                       letter-spacing:0.6px;text-transform:uppercase;\n                       margin:0 0 10px 0;padding:0;\">\n                Students are trained in areas including:\n              </p>\n\n              <!-- Skills block — minimal left-rule, no color -->\n              <table role=\"presentation\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\" style=\"mso-table-lspace:0pt;mso-table-rspace:0pt;margin-bottom:20px;\n                     border-left:5px solid #b74727;\">\n                <tr>\n                  <td style=\"padding:10px 16px;\">\n                    <p style=\"font-family:\'Source Sans 3\',\'Source Sans Pro\',Arial,\'Helvetica Neue\',Helvetica,sans-serif;\n                             font-size:13px;color:#333333;margin:0;padding:0;line-height:2.1;\">\n                      Data Analysis &amp; Statistical Modeling\n                      <span style=\"color:#bbbbbb;padding:0 7px;\">&#183;</span>\n                      Machine Learning &amp; Predictive Analytics\n                      <span style=\"color:#bbbbbb;padding:0 7px;\">&#183;</span>\n                      Data Engineering Fundamentals\n                      <span style=\"color:#bbbbbb;padding:0 7px;\">&#183;</span>\n                      Business Intelligence &amp; Visualization\n                      <span style=\"color:#bbbbbb;padding:0 7px;\">&#183;</span>\n                      Applied AI &amp; Emerging Technologies\n                    </p>\n                  </td>\n                </tr>\n              </table>\n\n              <p style=\"font-family:Merriweather,Georgia,\'Times New Roman\',Times,serif;\n                       font-size:15.5px;color:#333333;line-height:1.9;\n                       margin:0 0 16px 0;padding:0;\">\n                Depending on your organization&#8217;s requirements, our students are prepared to\n                contribute across\n                analytics, technology, research, or data-driven decision-support roles. For your\n                reference, <span style=\"color:#b74727;font-weight:500;\">we have\n                  attached the student profiles and placement brochure</span> to this email.\n              </p>\n\n              <p style=\"font-family:Merriweather,Georgia,\'Times New Roman\',Times,serif;\n                       font-size:15.5px;color:#333333;line-height:1.9;\n                       margin:0 0 0 0;padding:0;\">\n                We would be grateful for the opportunity to understand your hiring needs and explore\n                whether our\n                students may align with your current or upcoming requirements. If convenient, we would\n                be happy to\n                share further details or arrange a brief discussion at your preferred time. Thank you\n                for your time\n                and consideration.\n              </p>\n\n            </td>\n          </tr>\n          <!-- END BODY -->\n\n\n          <!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════\n             BLOCK 5 · HEAD OF DEPARTMENT — Right-Aligned Compact Signature\n        ══════════════════════════════════════════ -->\n          <tr>\n            <td style=\"padding:16px 32px;background-color:#ffffff;\">\n              <div style=\"text-align:right;\">\n                <table role=\"presentation\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"\n                  style=\"mso-table-lspace:0pt;mso-table-rspace:0pt;display:inline-table;margin:0;padding:0;\">\n                  <tr>\n                    <!-- Executive Details: Right-Aligned Stacked -->\n                    <td valign=\"center\" style=\"padding-right:12px;padding-left:0;width:auto;text-align:right;\">\n                      <!-- Name -->\n                      <p style=\"font-family:\'Segoe UI\',\'-apple-system\',\'Helvetica Neue\',Arial,sans-serif;\n                               font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#1a1a1a;\n                               line-height:1.2;margin:0 0 2px 0;padding:0;\n                               letter-spacing:-0.2px;text-align:right;\">\n                        <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/durba-bhattacharya-b3821773/\"\n                          style=\"color:#1a1a1a;text-decoration:none;\">\n                          <span style=\"color:#7a8fa3\">Warm Regards</span><br>\n                          Dr. Durba Bhattacharya\n                        </a>\n                      </p>\n\n                      <!-- Role -->\n                      <p style=\"font-family:\'Segoe UI\',\'-apple-system\',\'Helvetica Neue\',Arial,sans-serif;\n                               font-size:11px;font-weight:400;color:#888888;\n                               line-height:1.2;margin:0 0 2px 0;padding:0;\n                               letter-spacing:0px;text-align:right;\">\n                        Head of Department, Data Science\n                      </p>\n\n                      <!-- Institution -->\n                      <p style=\"font-family:\'Segoe UI\',\'-apple-system\',\'Helvetica Neue\',Arial,sans-serif;\n                               font-size:10px;font-weight:400;color:#999999;\n                               line-height:1.2;margin:0;padding:0;\n                               letter-spacing:0px;text-align:right;\">\n                        St. Xavier\'s College (Autonomous), Kolkata\n                      </p>\n                    </td>\n\n                    <!-- Profile Image: Small Circular (Right Side) -->\n                    <td valign=\"center\" style=\"padding-right:0;padding-left:12px;width:auto;min-width:40px;\">\n                      <img src=\"https://hr.holidayseva.com/Ass